description: Fight for your right to Comic Party! When Kazuki declares that he doesn't have a book to sell at the next Comic Party, he's free to wander around the doujinshi where he meeets Subaru Mikage, a kung fu supergirl who's vengeance is to fight all evil and save the world. Soon after their encounter, mayhem ensues when a bomb explodes, and together they join forces to create the Comi Rangers, a group of crime-fighters destined to protect the Comic Party from utter chaos. With time ticking away, the superheroes are out to fight for the right to Comic Party!
name: Vol. 2

description: Comi Rangers to the rescue! When Kazuki and company find Kingu Jacky's bomb, will they be able to put out the Comic Party pooper? Even if this TNT terrorist fizzles out, Kazuki must still figure out how to make his doujinshi light up the best-seller lists before he burns out. Meanwhile, will Mizuki turn the next Comic party into a costume party success? Stayed 'tooned'!
name: Vol. 3

description: When Asahi Sakurai--the lit chick who gave a poetry reading at Brother 2's booth--returns to the comic scene, it turns out that she's really a famous voice actress and singer in disguise! Kazuki helps her escape a crowd full of rabid fans, but discovers that this starlet is really a shy girl. Can he give her the confidence she needs to handle her fast-paced career? Later, Kazuki hits a wall in his doujinshi career, and must decide whether to stick with the parodies that have got him this far or expand into original work. Does he have the write stuff?
name: Vol. 4

description: When the Editor-in-Chief of a monthly manga magazine offers Kazuki a chance to become a professional manga artist, a fierce competition ensues between him and Eimi to see who is more fit for the job. Later, Mizuki wonders if there is room for her in Kazuki's busy life, while Kazuki is devastated after he sees Taishi embrace Mizuki. Is Kazuki in danger of losing Mizuki forever?
name: Vol. 5

description:
Volume 1 comprises two compelling stories. In 'The Door,' Manatsu is totally bored with life, so she decides to slit her wrists and end it all. However, her suicide attempt is unsuccessful. After Manatsu's released from the hospital, she meets another girl from school who is also suicidal. Because her arms are as skinny as asparagus stalks, Manatsu calls her 'Asparagus.' Together, Manatsu and Asparagus plot and plan a joint suicide. But, in the end, nothing goes according to plan...and when one of the friends dies, the other realizes that suicide isn't the answer, after all. In 'Mistakes,' Yoshioka is a teen prostitute and runaway who doesn't believe in love. Everything changes when she meets a street performer named Ryo who loves her for who she truly is. But when she turns one last trick to pay the bills, she risks losing everything. Will their love conquer all?!

Contents

  • The Door
  • Mistakes
name: Vol. 1

description:
One of the main reasons Chika Suzuki chose to attend her exclusive all-girls high school was its famous tennis coach. But this coach isn't exactly what she expected. He says and does things to the members of the team that could be seen as coercion and sexual harassment and when Chiha finally decides to tell her parents about it, she faces even more problems. The odds are against her, but she acts on the side of justice and bravely confronts a hot-button social issue that affects millions of women around the globe!

Back Blurb

The Shocking New Series from TOKYOPOP!

When your tennis coach puts the moves on you, do you report him to school officials?

Confidential Confessions delves into the life of a girl who battles the odds to seek justice. Suzuki chose to attend an exclusive all-girls high school solely based on the reputation of the famous tennis coach who works there. Every tennis player in the country dreams of training with him because he is the best of the best. But when the coach starts saying suggestive things to the players and touching them in inappropriate places, Suzuki is appalled---yet torn at the same time. Should she put up with the coach's perverted pawing just so she can continue to train with him? That's what the rest of the tennis team pressures her to do, and they say they won't support her if she tells the truth. But finally enough is enough, and Suzuki decides to come clean. When she reports the coach's lecherous behavior, the teachers refuse to take her seriously---and even call her a liar! With the odds are stacked against her, Suzuki stands her ground and bravely confronts a hot-button social issue that affects millions of women around the globe!

Confidential Confessions: A controversial manga that tackles society's most complex issues. Because real life doesn't always have a happy ending.
name: Tears

description: Kyoko is a pretty normal high school girl. She tries hard in school, but can't seem to get good grades, and her parents are putting a lot of pressure on her. She always feels left out, and she thinks she's fat. One day, she gets involved with a groups of kids who are doing drugs. She tries some speed, and at first she feels like she's on top of the world. She's able to stay up all night studying so she gets good grades, and she starts to slim down. But as she slides deeper and deeper into addiction, it gets harder and harder for her to get out, and she finds herself so desperate for drugs that she'd do anything for them. It will take all the love her parents and friends can muster to help her kick her habit.
name: Vol. 3

description:
This volume consists of four stories: 'Pain/ Ache': A 16 year-old girl becomes a prostitute (Enjo Kousai) and enjoys making easy money. It becomes her norm that sex comes with money, but she learns it's wrong and realize the gravity of her prostituting when she falls in love with her boyfriend. 'Kink/ Distortion': Aiko attends a junior high that has severe school regulations, and one of the teachers gives excessive descipline. Her friend Miho commits suicide after the teacher humiliates her in front of others. Aiko stands up and accuses the teacher of violating students' human rights. She's in for the battle of her life! 'Tomorrow': Ruka is the target of bullying girls in Nanako's class. No one says anything because everyone is afraid of being a target. But Nanako gets up the courage to stop the bullying after she begins to admire Ruka's silent bravery. 'Forbidden Kiss': Liliko is attracted to her friend Kanna. Since they're both girls, Kanna rejects Liliko at first. However, when Kanna begins to feel unloved by her family, she accepts Liliko's feelings for her and love blossoms.

Contents

  • Pain
  • Distortion
  • Tomorrow
  • Forbidden Kiss
name: Vol. 4

description:
Mika is a good girl from a loving family, but in the course of one terrible night, her normal life is shattered forever. Haunted by painful memories, Mika struggles to keep a secret that threatens to destroy everything she holds dear. Also in this volume: when a young girl's health begins to mysteriously deteriorate, her closest friends suddenly find themselves confronted with the cruel specter of HIV and AIDS.

Contents

  • Secret
  • Wish
name: Vol. 5

description:
Girls unite...and kick some butt! There's just no room for abusive boyfriends who also turn into stalkers. And when you're the new kid in school, someone has to stop bullies from harassing you! It's time to fight back and demand justice.

Contents

  • Secret
  • Wish
name: Vol. 6

description: This new comic series has been featured in Rolling Stone, E!, Elle Magazine, and thousands more sites. Is it the costume? The music? The Voice? Maybe it's all that stage blood. Whatever the reason, Lady Gaga has become one of the pop music's biggest stars. Bluewater Comics examines her impact on her legion of fans. Is there room for everyone in the Haus of GaGa?
name: Lady Gaga 2

description: A continuation of the gripping and cutting-edge Confidential Confessions, this series deals exclusively with the seedy underbelly of the sex industry. Using emotionally moving storylines and multi-dimensional characters, here is a shocking look into the hard-hitting issues that teens face today. Enlightening without being preachy, Confidential Confessions speaks to teens in a heartfelt, authentic way.
name: Vol. 1

description: What will happen to the "Peace" crew after two of their members turn against them? Will they be able to raise the one million yen they owe for their astronomical bar tab? And will they be able to stop selling their bodies before they end up losing their souls? The ultimate climax and conclusion in this confidential confession.
name: Vol. 2
Turkey Trouble
Keeping Up With The Softies
Min's Pest Show
Nervous Rex

description: Beginning an epic adventure showcasing the God of Thunder as you've never seen him before! The vassals of Asgard are in armed revolt...Odin is missing...Balder is dead...and the entire continent is battered by a years-long winter. How can Thor put the empire back together - especially with his mighty hammer Mjolnir mysteriously denied him?
name: Asgard, Part 1

description: Mercy Dante battles her way deeper into the pits of hell as she searches for "The Priest." Once a man of the cloth the Priest has been sentenced to an eternity inside the third ring of the Inferno, the circle reserved for the wrathful and the gluttonous. And he may be the only one who can guide Mercy further into hell as she searches for the man she must rescue. But when Dante makes her way inside of an eerie and unwelcoming church in the middle of the third ring she knows there is something very evil lurking and she must rely on her instincts in order to make it out in one piece.

Good Golly, Miss Dolly!

She's nubile, naughty, and quite pneumatic! She's Dolly, and she causes no en of mischief and mayhem in her wake! Men around the world are driven into a frenzy of eye-popping, jaw-dropping, and pants-expanding lust when ever Dolly happens by! It's not her fault - it's just the way she's built!

Written and illustrated by internationally renown fantasy artist Blas Gallego, Dolly represents a departure from Gallego's usual sphere of lush and magnificent paintings, and lets this most amazing artist indulge his lighter side. The resulting heroine defies both convention and gravity!

Collected for the first time are all the Dolly strips created by Blas Gallego, in all their fully painted full color glory. As an added feature, the space-faring adventures of the equally erotic Astraxy are also showcased.

You're never too old to love your Dolly!

volume.name: The Spanking Good Tales of Dolly

description: With a body built for sex, and a mind for solving crime (through the use of sex, of course), Magenta is a take-charge kind of woman! She needs no mutant ability or radioactive bug-bite to access her amazing abilities - a tight dress and some silky underwear will do! Any man (or mildly bi-curious woman) is putty in her hands, as Magenta uses her amazing sexuality to get to the bottom...of the case! Written by Celestino Pes and illustrated by Nik Guerra.
name: The Color of Sex

description: How ironic that the fate of the Internet, and the world, should fall on the shoulders of Yui - a technophobe of the first order. When the sentient computer virus, Grosser, infects the global network Com-Net, Yui is transported into cyberspace to combat his evil plans. Only by assembling the eight missing pieces of the corrector program can Yui make the Net safe once more. A dangerous quest, fabulous costumes, a cute sidekick... Yui's superhero dreams are about to come true where she least expected it!
name: Corrector Initialize

description: One great thing about entering the virtual reality of the Com-Net is that any dream really can come true. When Corrector Yui and the other Correctors explore the realm of Fairy Tale Net, they suddenly find themselves bringing their favorite fairy tales to life. But when Grosser and his henchmen discover them and threaten to delete the Correctors forever, it's time for the crusaders of justice to mount an attack. Joining their fight is a mysterious and handsome young prince. Who can think about love at a time like this? Why, Yui can, of course!
name: Lost in Cyberspace

description: With the help of her friends, the Corrector Programs, Yui is sent to the Marine Adventures digital theme park to do beta testing before the public is invited. But Yui's trip turns out to be more than a day at the beach when the evil virus Grosser turns up to infect the program. It'll take the song of a whale and the love of a girl to save this new realm of Com-Net.
name: A Song for Yui

description: When Yui was first transported to Com-Net to become a Corrector, her mentor, I.R., thought there was a mistake. Now it turns out he was right! Yui's best friend, Haruna, was meant to be the Corrector, but there was a serious mis-up. All is well, though, when Haruna gets a Corrector suit of her own, and she's so charming that all the Corrector programs instantly take a liking to her. Something's not right, though...why would Haruna encourage the Corrector programs to fight each other? Could it be the work of the evil Grosser?
name: Double Trouble

description: Corrector Yui is in her darkest hour. Although she has found all eight Corrector Programs, Yui must still face the fearsome CPU, Grosser. To make matters worse, her best friend, Haruna, has been turned to the dark side. The fate of Com-Net rests on Yui's shoulders in the final episode of this exciting shoujo adventure.
name: How the Web was Won

description: Eager to do their part in stemming the vampire invasion of San Francisco, the X-Men’s Science Team works to find a cure for vampirism. Bringing a vampire into their lab for examination, the scientists find themselves in over their heads when the monster escapes. With the lab on lockdown and a vampire on the loose, the X-Club is sure of only one thing: it’s going to take more than a doctoral degree in biochemistry to survive this night!

volume.name: X-Men: Curse of the Mutants - Smoke and Blood

description:
The Flintstones - The Winner! - 4 pages

The Flintstones - Holding The Bag! - 4 pages

The Flintstones - Did You Ever See A Dream Walking? - 6 pages - feat. The Gruesomes

The Flintstones - Fearless Fred - 8 pages

The Flintstones - Misery Master - 1 page - feat. Schleprock
name: The Winner!

description:
1. Kejsarörnen (Batman, Atom, Green Arrow, Joker, Two Face, Mahmoud Kahn / written by Bob Haney : translated from: Brave and the Bold #129-130)
 
2. Läderlappens Hemliga Identitet (Batman, Robin, Batgirl / written by Gardner Fox : translated from: Detective Comics #363)
name: Kejsarörnen

description: The adventures of the ultimate submissive, Buffy. She spends her time taking whatever punishment Mistress Justine dishes out.
name: Buffy

description:
Hae Jung Shin - a top student in her high school - leads a twisted and bizarre alternate life that no one could possibly imagine. After losing her mother, she's embittered by life and continuously feels victimized by the world. Her boyfriend, Jimmy, provides Hae Jung a sense of security despite their volatile relationship. Together they create a dysfunctional 'crazy' world, wherein they learn about the innocence and insanity of love. Enter Sung Moon Jin, an aspiring singer and fellow classmate of Hae Jung's and Jimmy's. He's always been infatuated with her from afar and when he finally meets her, he's determined to win her heart at any cost while at the same time recognizing that she lives in a world he can't relate to...although that doesn't stop him from trying to come between Hae Jung and her boyfriend. Bo Na, self-proclaimed 'best friend' of Hae Jung and part of their 'crazy' clique helps them make a fool out of Sung Moo, all for the sake of pure entertainment. 

Chapter Titles 

  • Vol. 1: My Mad Princess
  • Vol. 2: She Is "Mad in Heaven"
  • Vol. 3: Her Boyfriend, Jimmy
  • Vol. 4: No Risk, No Gain!
  • Vol. 5: Aspirin
  • Vol. 6: S-H-E
  • Vol. 7: Your Cruel Heart
  • Vol. 8: The Other Country
name: Vol. 1

description:
Sung Moo is a lone wolf who doesn't seem to care about anybody, but he's on the hunt for love and someone to care for him. On the other hand, all Jimmy cares about is money. He runs a division of his father's mafia business and extorts funds to produce movies. Stuck in the middle is Hae Jung, Jimmy's girlfriend, who is always being left alone with Sung Moo. This all spells a delicious--and dangerous--love triangle! 

Chapter Titles 

  • Vol. 9: Cultural Revolution
  • Vol. 10: My Funny History of Love
  • Vol. 11: Cultural Revolution
  • Vol. 12: Promise
  • Vol. 13: Twisted World Reach For the Summit
  • Vol. 14: Blood
  • Vol. 15: Stupid Paradiso
  • Vol. 16: Thunder Kiss
name: Vol. 2

description:
Hae Jung's hectic life is further complicated by the arrival of her stepmother's daughter, Julie, with whom she's had a rocky past. The situation doesn't improve when Jimmy decides to expose the truth of his past life and reflect on their "smoke and mirror"-filled relationship. Meanwhile, Sung Moo is contemplating giving up his dream of singing to pursue his other love: Hae Jung. 

Chapter Titles 

  • Vol. 17: Jimmy's History
  • Vol. 18: Yuri
  • Vol. 19: I've Forgotten Someone
  • Vol. 20: Lie and Let Die!!
  • Vol. 21: Look Back At Me!!
  • Vol. 22: What Do I Do?!
  • Vol. 23: Jimmy's Confession - Illusion and Lies
  • Vol. 24: Your Talent
  • Vol. 25: Cherry Cherry
name: Vol. 3

description:
Everyone finally comes clean! The truth about Bo Na's relationship with Hae Jung and Jimmy is revealed--find out how they met and what really happened between them! Learn about the deep, dark secret that Jimmy has been hiding all along...and discover Hae Jung's true feelings for Jimmy and Sung Moo! 

Chapter Titles 

  • Vol. 26: Bo Na's Story
  • Vol. 27: Candy
  • Vol. 28: I Like You
  • Vol. 29: Did My Heart Love Till Now
  • Vol. 30: Thank You!!
  • Vol. 31: Made in Hong Kong
  • Vol. 32: Yesterday Once More
  • Vol. 33: Sweet Dreams (Made Of This)
  • Vol. 34: Love, Then Fear
name: Vol. 4

description:
A farewell will become eternal love... A love stronger than Jimmy's life...he makes the decision to risk his life in order to protect Hae Jung! A farewell will become true love... Sung Moo's unchanging, absolute love in his decision to leave Hae Jung for everyone's sake! The crazy love song that will be cherished forever, its last concert!! 

Chapter Titles 

  • Vol. 35: Indian Summer Indian Dreams
  • Vol. 36: Love Is Stranger
  • Vol. 37: Another Sad Love Story Has Come To An End, and Yet Another One Has Just Begun
  • Vol. 38: Failure to Keep A Promise
  • Vol. 39: Lost Hiway - Goodbye
  • Vol. 40: I've Forgotten Him
  • Vol. 41: I Can't Stop Loving You
  • Vol. 42: I''ve Been Missing You
  • Vol. 43: Summer Dream
  • Vol. 44: Love Story Is Over
name: Vol. 5
